data.description: Welcome home to this renovated corner lot located in Cold Springs Ranch! The home boasts lots of indoor and outdoor living space with backyard access for RV parking or other toys. Upgrades include: updated toilets and faucets, interior and exterior paint, all new light fixtures, new laminate flooring, new  front fencing, and front yard landscaping. This home is within walking distance to BLM land and an even shorter drive to Village central Park and Cold Springs middle school.
